title: Episode 70: Ft DJ Mustard

DJ Mustard stops by and kicks it with Angela Yee, Gigi Maguire and Stephanie Santiago for a new episode of Lip Service. They discuss getting tied up, if initiating sex when on bad terms makes the situation better, sex after birth, posting breakups on social media and Mustard explains why he thinks lingerie is goofy.
